WheelForge — Web Application
Copyright (C) 2024–2026 WheelForge contributors

WheelForge is a Progressive Web App for configuring FFB wheel hardware
running Odrive-Wheel-compatible firmware.

Firmware is maintained separately at:
https://github.com/eagabriel/Odrive-Wheel

Unless otherwise noted in individual source files, this web application is
distributed under the GNU General Public License v3.0.

The full text of the GPLv3 is available at:
https://www.gnu.org/licenses/gpl-3.0.txt
